@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #E8E8E8

ProducerNode("Producer") --> KafkaNode("Broker1") : send
KafkaNode("Broker1") --> KafkaNode("Broker2") : replicate
KafkaNode("Broker1") --> KafkaNode("Broker3") : replicate
KafkaNode("Broker1") --> ConsumerNode("Consumer1") : fetch
KafkaNode("Broker2") --> ConsumerNode("Consumer2") : fetch

note top of ProducerNode : 生产者发送消息到指定主题
note top of KafkaNode : 消息被分区并复制到多个Broker
note top of ConsumerNode : 消费者从Broker中获取消息

@enduml
